product_desc:
We exist so that brilliant ideas don't go to waste. 

Students in the greater DC/Baltimore area are teeming with untapped potential. These students fully have the ability to grow their brilliant ideas into billion dollar companies, they just need a little bit of help to get started. A-Level Capital is the solution.

At A-Level Capital, our goal is to help a startup move through the first phase of its life with ease. With A-Level, a startup will have the ability to leverage our capital, talent, and skills to grow its company to the point where it can move on to attract funding on a larger scale. In addition, a new startup will have access to our wide network of connections, skills and mentors.
name: A-Level Capital
